data.description: WELCOME HOME TO 13702 Kodiak Brown Bear!!  Located in Kodiak Crossing just off Kennings Road, this beautiful 4 Bedroom, 2-1/2 Bathroom home offers quiet country living with quick access to Highway 90 allowing you to "jump on the road and go".  In addition to the spectacular open flow concept to this home, there are TWO upstairs gameroom/playroom areas that are perfect for entertaining the kiddos and the adults!  Formal dining room is currently being used as an office, but shows you the versatility of the area.  Come home after a long day of work and relax on your covered back patio and enjoy your fully fenced back yard!  LET'S GET YOU INTO YOUR BEAUTIFUL NEW HOME JUST IN TIME TO START MAKING FUN HOLIDAY MEMORIES.
